Display clear.
Transcript show: 'TBLOCK'.
Transcript cr.
Transcript show: ([ :x | x + 4 ] value: 3) printString.
Transcript cr.
Transcript show: ([ :x | [ :y | x + y ] value: 6 ] value: 5) printString.
Transcript cr.
true ifTrue: [ Transcript show: 'TCOND' ] ifFalse: [ Transcript show: 'BAD' ].
Transcript cr.
false ifFalse: [ Transcript show: 'FCOND' ].
Transcript cr.
